<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/471653-i-ve-just-started-reading-but-i-m-curious">I&#39;ve just started reading, but I&#39;m curious what everyone&#39;s opinion is on the amount of exposition and the length of the paragraphs in this book. Maybe I just don&#39;t read enough literary fiction, but it seems excessive. I do feel, however, that there&#39;s a sense of realism Cronin captures that is superior to most genre psi-fi / fantasy I&#39;ve read. Thoughts?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_471653'><a id="like_count_community_question_471653" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/471653?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">22 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F6690798-the-passage">like</a></span>

</li>
