      GoodReads GiveAway
  </div>


    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer91933704" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8316090398084415985">Thank you, GoodReads for this Advance Reader&apos;s Edition. So hard to rate. Act I is simply superb - brilliantly written, suspenseful, beautiful, a full 5. Act II is cluttered, (too) many actors moving on and off stage, rarely doing anything of consequence while they are there. Act III is a combination screenplay, set-up for a sequel, exciting in a dystopian, end-of-days sort of way, (with a ray or two of hope).</span>
  <span id="freeText8316090398084415985" style="display:none">Thank you, GoodReads for this Advance Reader's Edition. So hard to rate. Act I is simply superb - brilliantly written, suspenseful, beautiful, a full 5. Act II is cluttered, (too) many actors moving on and off stage, rarely doing anything of consequence while they are there. Act III is a combination screenplay, set-up for a sequel, exciting in a dystopian, end-of-days sort of way, (with a ray or two of hope).</span>
